spyGLass' basic concept is based on the idea presented by ogldebug, a
program distributed with Silicon Graphic's IRIX Operating System and
used to debug OpenGL programs.  spyGLass is not related to ogldebug
beyond that point, specifically, it does not contain any of ogldebug's
source code.
